\fs60\fsmilli30400 \cf7 Getting Started\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf7 This page will help you get started with Agoda-Demand. You'll be up and running in a jiffy!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\fs30 \cf7 Agoda offers a wide range of hotels worldwide, including those from Priceline, making it a great choice for both business and leisure travelers. We're always working to add more options from our Agoda Supply Partners. Our API provides competitive rates and high-quality content for a vast number of listings. As a fully online, self-service platform, we offer all our self-service features to partners through APIs, mirroring the functionalities on the Agoda website. This flexible setup lets you integrate only the features that fit your business needs.\
With our extensive experience in both B2C and B2B integration services, we're here to support you through the technical integration process until launch. We also offer ongoing support for marketing and revenue optimization.\
Here are five easy steps to start partnering with us:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	1	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Find the partnership model that suits you best.\
\ls4\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Review our API and begin integration.\
\ls4\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	3	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Become a partner to receive your site credentials.\
\ls4\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	4	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Request certification from our team.\
\ls4\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	5	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Once ready, switch to our Live environment.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs52\fsmilli26250 \cf7 Agoda Partnership Models\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 Interested in becoming our partner or unsure which partnership model suits you best? Feel free to get in touch with our Account Manager .\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs37\fsmilli18750 \cf7 Online Affiliates/MSE model\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 {{\NeXTGraphic a2407c3-image-2024-1-3_9-7-16.png \width7200 \height1980 \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}洞\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf7 Let's start with the simplest integration model. If your website is an online affiliate or MSE site that aggregates and compares hotel prices from various online travel agencies, we offer the Online Affiliates / MSE model. This model features a lightning-fast availability/rate API, providing essential information to display on your website with easy integration and minimal development.\uc0\u8232 The only API you need to implement for this model is the Search API.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs37\fsmilli18750 \cf7 Agoda Fulfill Assisted model\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 {{\NeXTGraphic cea1e57-image-2024-1-3_9-7-29.png \width7200 \height1920 \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}洞\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf7 If you don't have post-booking customer services but want to integrate your booking form with our Book API, the Agoda Fulfill Assisted Model is perfect for you. With this model, Agoda will directly charge your customers, provide post-booking customer services, and send hotel vouchers to your customers.\uc0\u8232 The APIs to be implemented for this model are the Search API and the Book API.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs37\fsmilli18750 \cf7 Partner Fulfillment model\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 {{\NeXTGraphic Attachment.png \width320 \height320 \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}洞\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf7 If you want to take full control of the booking flow, including post-booking customer services, the Partner Fulfillment Model is the best option. In this model, you'll have access to our customer services APIs, such as the Cancellation API and Special Requests API. You will handle payments and provide post-booking customer services directly to your end customers.\uc0\u8232 The APIs to be implemented for this model are the Search API, Book API, and optionally, the Post Book API.\u8232 (optional)\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs52\fsmilli26250 \cf7 How does the integration work?\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\fs40 \cf7 \strokec12 1\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs45 \cf13 \strokec13 Content\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs30 \cf7 \strokec7 Gain access to property content from around the world. We strongly recommend refreshing property content daily. Learn how to integrate our Content API.\
\pard\pardeftab720\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\fs40 \cf7 \strokec12 2\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs45 \cf13 \strokec13 Search\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs30 \cf7 \strokec7 The Search API lets you retrieve available rooms and rates at each property. Break down hotels into smaller search requests, send them in parallel, and then assemble the responses to construct your search results page.\
\pard\pardeftab720\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\fs40 \cf7 \strokec12 3\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs45 \cf13 \strokec13 Book\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs30 \cf7 \strokec7 Use the Book API to submit the details of the room you want from our search response, along with guest information and payment details.\cf14 \strokec14 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf14 Since allotments and prices are dynamic, we recommend calling the Pre-check API in the background to ensure rates and availability are still valid.\
Special requests can be submitted after booking, but they are not guaranteed and depend on the property's ability to fulfill them.\
\pard\pardeftab720\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\fs40 \cf7 \strokec12 4\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs45 \cf13 \strokec13 Report\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs30 \cf7 \strokec7 Retrieve all bookings made with us and get detailed information on each booking. Explore the features available in our Post-book API.\
\pard\pardeftab720\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\fs40 \cf7 \strokec12 5\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs45 \cf13 \strokec13 Cancel\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs30 \cf7 \strokec7 Need to cancel a booking? Our two-step Cancel API allows you to review the cancellation policy and confirm if you are certain about canceling the booking.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \
