\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 We begin with a feasibility study to evaluate the potential for success, covering areas such as technical, operational, and commercial requirements. Once these areas have been thoroughly examined, we can align and start the project.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

