\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 Next, you will integrate with our API as needed. To avoid delays from fixing your website, we strongly recommend following our best practices during development. You are fully responsible for developing and performing system testing on your website.\
