\ls5\ilvl0\cf7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Finance Account Creation:\'a0Agoda needs to create a new finance account for you. Two important documents required are the signed contract and the signed vendor registration form (AVRF).\
\ls5\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Resource Allocation:\'a0Agoda needs to allocate resources for incoming traffic based on capacity demand. Therefore, you and the Agoda connectivity team need to plan the expected traffic to ensure resources are available once the website launches.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
