\fs60\fsmilli30400 \cf7 \strokec7 Environment Setup\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \

\fs52\fsmilli26250 Introduction\

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 Welcome to Agoda's sandbox environment! This is your go-to space for creating test bookings. Our sandbox servers mirror our production servers but with limited capacity. We encourage all partners to thoroughly test in the sandbox before moving to the live environment. Please remember, testing in the live environment requires explicit approval from your Agoda Account Manager.\uc0\u8232 Unauthorized test bookings in the live environment may result in a\'a0non-refundable cancellation fee.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \

\fs52\fsmilli26250 Short TTL for DNS\

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 To ensure top-notch service quality on our APIs, we recommend setting a time-to-live (TTL) of 5 minutes or less on DNS servers and applications connecting to Agoda API URLs. This helps us quickly switch between data centers if one becomes unavailable, ensuring seamless service.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \

\fs52\fsmilli26250 HTTP Header\

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \

\f1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs37\fsmilli18750 \cf7 Authorization\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 Every request must include an Authorization Header with your siteid and apikey, separated by a colon. This must match the siteid and apikey in the request body. The Authorization header is mandatory for all API requests.\uc0\u8232 Example Authorization header:\
\pard\pardeftab720\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs27 \cf7 \cb16 \strokec7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f5 \cf7 Authorization: 123456:00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \cb1 \strokec7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs37\fsmilli18750 \cf7 Accept-Encoding\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 To save bandwidth and speed up your site, we recommend enabling compression. Set the HTTP request header for compression as follows:\
\pard\pardeftab720\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs27 \cf7 \cb16 \strokec7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f5 \cf7 Accept-Encoding: gzip,deflats\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \cb1 \strokec7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs37\fsmilli18750 \cf7 TLS Protocol\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 For security and to comply with PCI Security Industry Standards, ensure your production system uses TLS v1.2.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs37\fsmilli18750 \cf7 Sandbox Environment URLs\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 Your test site credentials are set up to access all features of our API in the Agoda Sandbox environment. For details, please contact your account manager.\uc0\u8232 If you're an existing partner with site credentials, you can start making requests to our Sandbox endpoints. After passing our certification process and receiving approval to go live, simply switch your request endpoints to the production ones provided later, with no additional code changes needed.\u8232 Interested in becoming a partner and obtaining your own site credentials? Reach out to our\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://partners.agoda.com/DeveloperPortal/APIDoc/ContactUs"}}{\fldrslt \cf5 \ul \ulc5 \strokec5 Account Manager}}\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs37\fsmilli18750 \cf7 SSL Certificate\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 We accept most globally recognized SSL Certificate Authorities. However, it's best to confirm with your Agoda representative.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

