\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 Welcome to Agoda! We offer hotel content in two different formats to suit your needs. Your account manager will provide the URL to download either the Data File or Data Feed.\
