\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 Format:\'a0CSV\uc0\u8232 Customization:\'a0Available in your preferred currency and language\u8232 Scope:\'a0Includes only hotel-level information\u8232 Usage:\'a0Ideal for collecting and storing hotel data or initializing a database\u8232 Recommendation:\'a0Refresh the data file at least once a week\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
