\fs60\fsmilli30400 \cf7 \strokec7 Book API\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \

\fs52\fsmilli26250 Introduction\

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 By integrating the Book API, partners can send book requests to Agoda in JSON format.\uc0\u8232 We offer two URL endpoints: the mandatory Book API for making bookings and the optional Precheck API.\u8232 Since hotel rates and availability are dynamic, price changes and allotment updates can cause booking failures. Therefore, we highly recommend using the Precheck API to verify the selected offer's validity right before sending the book request.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \

\fs52\fsmilli26250 Precheck API\

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 The Precheck service aims to boost booking success rates by allowing partners to verify allotments and rates before sending a booking request. This can be done in the background while the customer enters their personal details in the booking form.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls29\ilvl0\cf7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Successful Precheck:\'a0If the Precheck response is successful, the customer will enjoy a smooth booking process.\
\ls29\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Failed Precheck:\'a0If the Precheck response fails, partners can inform customers to choose a different room offer.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \strokec7 Two scenarios can cause a Precheck to fail, and partners should halt the booking request:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls30\ilvl0\cf7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	1	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Price Changes:\'a0Prices may change due to hotel owners updating rates, especially during peak seasons (status code = 501).\
\ls30\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Room Unavailability:\'a0The room may no longer be available because it was booked by another customer or partner moments ago (status codes = 502 or 503).\
\ls30\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	3	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Other scenarios where partners should continue with the booking request include:\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls30\ilvl1\cf7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Successful Precheck:\'a0Allotment and price are still available (status code = 200).\
\ls30\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Timeouts:\'a0If the Precheck response takes longer than 60 seconds, partners should proceed with the booking request. Technical errors may occur internally or externally.\
\ls30\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Other Errors:\'a0Ignore technical errors and proceed with the booking request.\uc0\u8232 Partners should implement the logic: IF status code is 501, 502, or 503, THEN ask the customer to find a different room offer; ELSE continue with the booking request.\u8232 For detailed request and response information or a full API description; click here to see a sample.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

