\f1\fs30 \cf7 To improve usability and navigation, we have reorganized our Post Booking API documentation into dedicated subpages for each key function. This allows you to quickly find the information you need for specific post-booking actions.\
The Post Booking API enables you to manage your bookings after they have been created. You can retrieve booking details, amend existing bookings, send special requests, or cancel bookings as needed.\uc0\u8232 Each of these actions now has its own dedicated page, making it easier to explore the available endpoints, parameters, and response examples.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

