\fs60\fsmilli30400 \cf7 \strokec7 Amend Bookings\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \

\fs52\fsmilli26250 Introduction\

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 This document outlines the ability to amend bookings via API, eliminating the need for customer service intervention.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \

\fs52\fsmilli26250 New APIs\

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 \'95\'a0Amendment API: Allows users to request amendments. This API sets up the requested amendment, validates its feasibility, and provides refund or additional charge details for date changes.\uc0\u8232 \'95\'a0ConfirmAmendment API: Confirms and processes the requested amendment\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \

\fs52\fsmilli26250 Changes to Existing API\

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 \'95\'a0Booking Details API: Now includes options for available amendments and displays the amendment history for bookings that have already been modified.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \

\fs52\fsmilli26250 Allowed Amendments\

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 \'95 Date change\uc0\u8232 \'95 Name change\u8232 \'95 Special request\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \

\fs52\fsmilli26250 Important Notes\

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls59\ilvl0
\f1\fs30 \cf7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 The list of permitted amendments for a booking can be found in the Booking Details API, under the\'a0
\f5\fs27 \cb16 amendmentFeatures
\f1\fs30 \cb1 \'a0field. Partners should always check this field before attempting any booking amendments through the Amendment API.\
\ls59\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Only one amendment can be processed at a time. For example, a partner cannot amend both the date and guest information simultaneously.\
\ls59\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Some fields, such as Guest Name, may be amendable even if others, like check-in or check-out dates, are not. The ability to amend is determined by individual field flags.\
\ls59\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 For guest name changes, there is no validation on the nationality of new guests. Partners must ensure the nationality matches the original booking.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \strokec7 \

\fs52\fsmilli26250 Mandatory header fields:\

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 \'95 API Key\uc0\u8232 \'95 SiteId\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \

\fs52\fsmilli26250 Amendment API\

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 The Amendment API allows partners to request changes to a booking. This API validates the requested amendment and returns information about any additional charges or refunds that may apply.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

