\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \

\fs52\fsmilli26250 Affiliate API Usage Guide: Fee Waiver Cancellation\

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 This document provides guidance on using the Affiliate APIs for handling booking cancellations with a fee waiver.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \

\fs52\fsmilli26250 Important Notes\

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 Before proceeding with the API implementation and testing, please carefully review the following important notes:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls71\ilvl0\cf7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	1	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Testing Environment:\uc0\u8232 Please ensure that only the provided testing environment URL is used for testing purposes. Prior to testing, contact the Agoda Technical Manager to enable the necessary permissions. Any losses incurred from using the production environment during the testing phase will need to be absorbed and handled independently.\
\ls71\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Responsible Use of Fee Waiver Cancellation:\uc0\u8232 The Fee Waiver Cancellation feature should be used responsibly and in alignment with the actual needs of the guest. Misuse or excessive use of this interface is strictly forbidden.\
\ls71\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	3	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Hotel's Final Decision on Fee Waiver Cancellation:\uc0\u8232 The result of a Fee Waiver Cancellation request is subject to the final decision of the hotel. Agoda cannot guarantee that the fee waiver request will be approved.\
