\fs60\fsmilli30400 \cf7 \strokec7 Best Practices & Certification Process\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf7 To achieve certification, please adhere to our policy and display the required items on your production system. Ensure you meet all necessary requirements to avoid potential delays in going live due to needed adjustments.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \

\fs52\fsmilli26250 1. Prohibited Countries Policy\

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 We do not operate in or have any affiliations with the following countries: Cuba, Syria, Sudan, Iran, and North Korea. Consequently, you will not find hotels from these countries in our system, and bookings from customers in these regions will be rejected.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \

\fs52\fsmilli26250 2. Sandbox Environment\

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls82\ilvl0
\f1\fs30 \cf7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Our sandbox servers are identical to our production servers, but any booking requests made to\'a0will not result in actual hotel reservations or credit card charges.\
\ls82\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Use the sandbox environment to test functionality and verify data, then re-verify in the live environment.\
\ls82\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 The JSON request format in the sandbox is less strict than in the live environment, so minor errors might pass in the sandbox but not in production.\
\ls82\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 All JSON requests must strictly follow the API specifications, such as using guest titles like \'93Mr.\'94, \'93Ms.\'94, \'93Mrs.\'94, or \'93Dr.\'94 only.\
\ls82\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
