\fs45 \cf7 \strokec7 8. Booking Confirmation Flow\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \strokec7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 Agoda highly recommends implementing the booking confirmation flow to minimize post-booking check-in issues.\uc0\u8232 After sending a booking request, wait up to 120 seconds (booking cutoff time). Agoda will try to reserve the allotment(s) and confirm the booking. Processing time varies due to several factors.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls88\ilvl0\cf7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 When partners receive Agoda BookingID and itineraryID from BookAPI, the booking is considered confirmed.\
\ls88\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 To get booking details or status, call our POST BOOKING API (BookingListAPI/BookingdetailsAPI).\
\ls88\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Wait at least 1 minute before calling POST BOOKING API after receiving a response from BOOKAPI, and implement a retry logic: at least 3 times in 15 minutes.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \strokec7 Some partners may want to include calling BookingListAPI/Bookingdetails API in their confirmation flow. Discuss this with your Agoda Technical Account Manager before going live.\uc0\u8232 This practice depends on the partner's system flow. Statistically, 90% of bookings are confirmed within a minute, and 98% within an hour. If confirmation is not received in an acceptable time frame, contact Agoda Customer Service to manually confirm the booking.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

