\f1\fs30 \cf7 BookingDetail API supports up to 40 booking IDs. Set a wait time of 30 seconds with a minimum of 3 retries in case of timeout.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs45 \cf7 \strokec7 12. Cancel a booking\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \strokec7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 To cancel a booking, complete two steps:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls89\ilvl0\cf7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Cancellation API and Confirm_cancellation API. BookingID, Reference, and RefundRateInclusive must match to proceed.\
\ls89\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 ConfirmCancellationAPI can proceed after receiving the cancellation response.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \strokec7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs45 \cf7 \strokec7 13. Child and Extra beds policy\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \strokec7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 Notify customers of any additional costs for extra beds and the age definition for children.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls90\ilvl0\cf7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 If a child stays on existing bedding (free of charge), room benefits are not provided. Customers will pay additional charges directly to the hotel, e.g., for breakfast.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \strokec7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs45 \cf7 \strokec7 14. Special Request\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \strokec7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 There are two ways to submit special requests:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls91\ilvl0\cf7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	1	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Include 'SpecialRequest' in Book API.\
\ls91\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Submit separately via Special Request API, waiting 30 seconds after receiving the booking ID.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \strokec7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs45 \cf7 \strokec7 Certification Process\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \strokec7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 The certification process ensures your integration is fully prepared to serve customers on your live production servers. You must pass certification and receive approval from us before your application can go live and handle bookings.\uc0\u8232 Criteria:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls92\ilvl0\cf7 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Hotel Database:\'a0Ensure hotels and room information are correctly mapped and regularly updated.\
\ls92\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Special Hotel Content:\'a0Display any hotel remarks clearly to users.\
\ls92\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Searching:\'a0Implement hotel list search properly and capture search results accurately.\
\ls92\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Booking:\'a0Calculate the total price correctly, and prominently display any excluded surcharges.\
\ls92\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Booking Status:\'a0Implement and handle the booking confirmation flow correctly.\
\ls92\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Cancellation:\'a0Implement the two-step cancellation process and ensure bookings can be successfully canceled.\
\ls92\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Reporting:\'a0Retrieve booking reports using the BookingList and BookingDetail APIs.\
\ls92\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 Customer Voucher:\'a0Always display Agoda Booking ID as the reference to ensure hotel can find the booking.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \strokec7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs45 \cf7 \strokec7 Agoda Self-Service Portal\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf7 \strokec7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf7 We offer a self-service portal for partners to manage and modify their bookings online. Through this portal, you can update booking information, check booking status, and handle changes efficiently\'97all in one place.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf7 If you would like access to the self-service portal, please contact your technical account manager directly. Our team will assist you with the onboarding process and answer any questions you may have.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

